---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Arca"
	description="Arca runs your operations. Built by Mal Mposha for small service businesses who are done fighting their own systems."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-04-24')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Arca is an operations platform for small service businesses — coaches, consultants, agencies,
		and solo operators who have outgrown their current setup but do not want to hire a full ops team.
	</p>

	<p>
		We handle scheduling, invoicing, client onboarding, and follow-ups from a single conversational
		interface. No dashboards to learn. No CRMs to configure. You describe what you need, we build it
		and run it.
	</p>

	<p>
		The platform is built on a multi-agent architecture: a client-facing agent handles conversations
		while a background team of specialized agents manages scheduling, billing, content, and research.
		Everything is coordinated through a single ops board that tracks work from request to delivery.
	</p>

	<p>
		Arca was founded by Mal Mposha, operator of Unbanked, a private holding company building
		practical tools for service businesses. The goal is simple: replace the ops chaos with a system
		that actually works.
	</p>

	<p>
		Current pricing starts at $97 per month for the Starter tier, with white-glove onboarding and
		fully managed operations available at higher tiers. Most clients are live within 7 days of signup.
	</p>
</Layout>
